    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are absolutely no scratches, dents, or stone chips to be found. Inside, the cabin remains pristine, with the leather upholstery still firm and free of any creases or wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open checkbook. It comes with a complete service history and is ready for a collector or an enthusiast who demands the very best.",
