      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that presents exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Every inch of the exterior gleams with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of swirl marks, stone chips, or any visible imperfections. The car has been exclusively garage-kept and professionally detailed, featuring a high-end ceramic coating that preserves its breathtaking luster. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats are supple and show absolutely no signs of wear on the bolsters, still retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and digital display functions with crisp, tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed only by certified specialists with a full paper trail included. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved specimen for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
